title: After Signing in for 30 Days, I Can Annihilate Stars
description: After Signing in for 30 Days, I Can Annihilate Stars When otherworldly demons invaded, thousands of Heroes were chosen to enter a secret realm. Their bloody struggles against demon beasts were streamed live for the whole world to see. Unfortunately, I, Chu Mo, was among the chosen ones. But all the other Heroes are frigging cultivators! You want a normal guy like me to go fight demons? Are you insane?! Then, the sign-in system went online. On my 1st day of signing in, I got the power of a 1000 year old demom beast; on the 2nd, I received a legendary Martial Gods experience; and on the 30th day, I turned into planet-class one-punch man! Qian Dao 30 Tian Yi Quan Bao Xing OP After 30 Days Of Sign-In Qiān Dào 30 Tiān Yī Quán Bào Xīng Signed 30 Days and I Can Destroy a Star With One Punch 签到30天一拳爆星
